Turki Al - Sheikh ignites social media because of the night dream .. Learn details
04 Nov 2019, 06:52 by ElBalad
Turki Al-Sheikh published a post on the social networking site "Facebook", which angered the audience of Zamalek, and launched a number of pioneers of the social networking site Twitter hashtag # Turki_al_ Sheikh.Hashtag ranked first in the list of most traded on Twitter .. The most prominent tweets are as follows: #Turki_alalshikh #Turki_alalshikh #Turki_alalshikh #Turki_alalshikh #Turki_alalshikh #Turki_alalshikh #Turki_alalshikh #Turki_alalshikh #Turki_alalshikh #Turki_alalshikh #Turki_alalshikh Through the social networking site "Facebook" aroused anger "I grew up and dreamed of the dream of God, I make it good and I want you to explain it to me," he wrote. "I dreamed that I would eat a night of Arabic called Al-Shahat. It tasted sweet."
